features.text: Photograph By: Alexander Harold AKA Creative Connect

This release will be an exclusive photo from the set of 6lack ft J Cole’s “Pretty Little Fears” Video Shoot. This is a 1 of 1 photo and is the same photo on the RIAA Certified Platinum Plaque (Over Million Copies Sold For This Song). This photo was taken at the now closed “Fantasy Island” in Buffalo NY. The music video has over 125 million views currently.

Part of the profit will go to supporting artists consulted by Black Brooklyn by helping with minting and gas fees.
